## Spacing System

### Base Unit
- **8px base unit** for all spacing
- Consistent scaling: 4px, 8px, 12px, 16px, 24px, 32px, 48px, 64px, 80px
- Use spacing tokens throughout
- Maintain proportional relationships

### Spacing Guidelines
- **Between related elements**: 8px-16px
- **Between sections**: 24px-48px
- **Page margins**: 16px-24px (mobile), 32px-48px (desktop)
- **Component padding**: 16px-24px

### Code Example
```tsx
// ‚úÖ CORRECT - Use spacing tokens
<div className="space-y-6"> {/* 24px spacing */}
  <section className="p-4"> {/* 16px padding */}
    <h2 className="mb-3">Title</h2> {/* 12px margin */}
  </section>
</div>
```

