## Grid System

### 12-Column Grid
- **Desktop**: 12-column grid with 24px gutters
- **Max-width**: 1200px for content
- **Mobile**: 100% width, single column
- Flexible gutters that adapt to screen size

### Grid Usage
- Use grid for complex layouts
- Use flexbox for simple layouts
- Maintain consistent column widths
- Responsive breakpoints

### Code Example
```tsx
// ‚úÖ CORRECT - Grid layout
<div className="grid grid-cols-12 gap-6 max-w-1200 mx-auto">
  <div className="col-span-12 md:col-span-8">Main content</div>
  <div className="col-span-12 md:col-span-4">Sidebar</div>
</div>
```

