## White Space Rules

### White Space Guidelines
- **Minimum**: 20% white space on page
- **Between related elements**: 24px
- **Between sections**: 48px
- Use white space strategically to highlight important content

### Visual Balance
- Distribute visual weight evenly
- Use symmetry and asymmetry strategically
- Create breathing room
- Prevent visual clutter

